213bf8d37dbc88b9c222e1b38a78ede528fedcd0.query:
INSERT INTO messages (id, user_id, content)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
            ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE
            SET user_id = $2, content = $3

97800f1c8002ae71e100f5bcb60011930eac244b.query:
SELECT username, display_name
            FROM users
            WHERE id = $1

a820efa0679701672eb52b5469c0e2ee49beb211.query:
INSERT INTO users (id, username, display_name)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
            ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE
            SET username = $2, display_name = $3

c4fc5cb66c404905a2040d36ddf5e90aacc5763e.query:
INSERT INTO secrets (user_id, password, last_changed) VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
            ON CONFLICT (user_id) DO UPDATE SET password = $2, last_changed = $3

ec6ec14c14e0f907aec486a3bd403ca64d52d62c.query:
SELECT user_id, content
            FROM messages
            WHERE id = $1

f693ff27c21576f4749e4763f8be8dba1048cd93.query:
SELECT id, username, display_name
            FROM users
            WHERE username = $1

fc7ecd98dad2144f8f01d9ec80c4d992c017cb00.query:
SELECT users.id, secrets.password, secrets.last_changed
            FROM users JOIN secrets ON users.id = secrets.user_id
            WHERE users.username = $1
